reviewText: As usual item delivered on time and in good condition.great cd Toby Keith never fails to produce good music

Toby Keith is a treat - such a sense of humor, and it's contagious.
He's a great singer, and loves to fun it up, and it's fun to watch.

I have always liked Toby Keith's music, but these 5 videos are not only
good music but very entertaining and VERY funny MUSIC VIDEOS. You won't
go wrong buying this DVD.
Saw Toby And the Band Live in 2005....Great Performance!.....Toby needs to put out a Live Concert DVD Already!

I SAW THE TOBY KEITH/TED NUGENT CONCERT FEB. 19TH, 2005.  I THEN WENT OUT AND PURCHASED THIS MUSIC DVD, ALONG WITH ANYTHING ELSE I COULD FIND THAT HAD TOBY KEITH IN IT!  THE MUSIC DVD IS GREAT!

JUST WISH I COULD FIND MORE MUSCI DVDS OF TOBY KEITH!  HE IS AWESOME!

KJB
